{"id":547404,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/12/【立此存照】出现雷洋案三字微博全部自动禁/","date":"2016-12-24T03:51:53Z","modified":"2016-12-24T08:42:06Z","title":"【立此存照】出现“雷洋案”三字微博全部自动禁止评论","content":"<p>雷洋案涉事警员不起诉的消息发出后，中共当局对网络舆论进行了<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/12/%e3%80%90%e7%9c%9f%e7%90%86%e9%83%a8%e3%80%91-83/\" target=\"_blank\">严格控制</a>。有新浪微博用户今日发现，任何微博内容内只要包含“雷洋案”三个字，就会被自动禁止评论。已有其他网民对此进行试验，验证了这个说法。</p>\n<blockquote><p><strong>相关阅读</strong>：<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/12/%e3%80%90%e7%9c%9f%e7%90%86%e9%83%a8%e3%80%91-83/\" target=\"_blank\">【真理部】“北京检方:不起诉雷洋案五名涉案警务人员”</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/6187648agw1fb12hq29v5j20qo1bfwkm.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-547413\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/6187648agw1fb12hq29v5j20qo1bfwkm.jpg\" alt=\"6187648agw1fb12hq29v5j20qo1bfwkm\" width=\"400\" height=\"711\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/6187648agw1fb12hq29v5j20qo1bfwkm.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/6187648agw1fb12hq29v5j20qo1bfwkm-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/6187648agw1fb12hq29v5j20qo1bfwkm-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>以下为包含“雷洋案”的微博被自动禁评的截图，由中国数字时代编辑收集：</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/顾猷.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-547411\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/顾猷.jpg\" alt=\"%e9%a1%be%e7%8c%b7\" width=\"500\" height=\"460\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/顾猷.jpg 1210w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/顾猷-300x276.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/顾猷-768x706.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/顾猷-1024x941.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigita